# Tech Stack and Reference Guide

## Docs (This Site)

- [SvelteKit](https://kit.svelte.dev/docs) — App framework
- [Wrangler](https://developers.cloudflare.com/workers/wrangler/) — Cloudflare CLI and dev server
- [Cloudflare Pages](https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/) — Hosting and deployment

## Front End

- [React](https://react.dev/) + [TypeScript](https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/) — UI framework
- [Vite](https://vitejs.dev/guide/) — Build tool and dev server
- [Apollo Client](https://www.apollographql.com/docs/react/) — GraphQL client
- [shadcn/ui](https://ui.shadcn.com/docs/installation) + [Tailwind CSS](https://tailwindcss.com/docs/) — Styling
- [Recharts](https://recharts.github.io/) — Price charts
- [GraphQL](https://graphql.org/learn/) with codegen — Data requests and subscriptions

## API

- [Python](https://docs.python.org/3/) — Backend language
- [FastAPI](https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/) — HTTP framework
- [Strawberry](https://strawberry.rocks/docs) — GraphQL schema and resolvers
- [Better Auth](https://www.better-auth.com/docs/introduction) — Authentication (JWT)

## Infrastructure

- [Docker Compose](https://docs.docker.com/compose/) — Container orchestration
- [Redis](https://redis.io/docs/) — Celery broker and result backend
- [Celery](https://docs.celeryq.dev/en/stable/) — Task queue and cron scheduling
- [PostgreSQL](https://www.postgresql.org/docs/) — Relational database
- [SQLAlchemy](https://docs.sqlalchemy.org/en/20/) — Python ORM and async driver
- [Alembic](https://alembic.sqlalchemy.org/en/latest/) — Database migrations

## External APIs

- [Scryfall API](https://scryfall.com/docs/api) — Card data and pricing

## Testing and QA

- [ESLint](https://eslint.org/docs/latest/) — JavaScript/TypeScript linting
- [Prettier](https://prettier.io/docs/en/index.html) — Code formatting
- [pytest](https://docs.pytest.org/en/stable/) — Python test framework
- [Playwright](https://playwright.dev/docs/intro) — End-to-end browser testing
